problems.description:
Use Spring Data JPA custom queries and projections.

```java
// Interface projection — only fetch needed columns:
public interface UserSummary {
    String getName();
    String getEmail();
}

@Repository
public interface UserRepository extends JpaRepository<User, Long> {
    // Derived query:
    List<User> findByRoleAndActiveTrue(Role role);

    // Custom JPQL:
    @Query("SELECT u FROM User u WHERE u.createdAt > :since ORDER BY u.createdAt DESC")
    Page<User> findRecentUsers(@Param("since") LocalDateTime since, Pageable pageable);

    // Projection:
    List<UserSummary> findByDepartmentId(Long deptId);
}
```

**Key insight:** Projections fetch only specified columns — faster than full entity load. Derived queries auto-generate SQL from method names.

